text: Tanzilya Zarbieva (born 8 February 1991) is an Uzbekistani footballer who plays as a defender for the Uzbekistan women's national team. ==References== == External links == * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Uzbekistani women's footballers Category:Uzbekistan women's international footballers Category:People from Jizzakh Category:Uzbekistani women's futsal players
